91
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:16,350
Tell me ... Tell me everything you know about Kang Mi Na.

92
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:19,590
Who is that woman?

93
00:07:23,190 --> 00:07:25,700
A while ago,

94
