 Jo Yeon Ju. 

97
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:36,040
   

98
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:38,400
It had a hospital's name instead of a pharmacy's name,

99
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:40,910
