100
00:07:40,910 --> 00:07:43,610
Apparently my wife has records in one of their wards.

101
00:07:43,610 --> 00:07:45,210
I went and asked right away.

102
00:07:45,210 --> 00:07:47,070
 Which room is patient Jo Yeon Ju in? 

103
00:07:47,070 --> 00:07:48,840
 I want to visit her. 

104
