When I was young, I was often called to emergency rooms.

125
00:09:12,610 --> 00:09:14,840
"Your father was stabbed,"

126
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:18,090
or "your father punched someone into a paste."

127
00:09:18,090 --> 00:09:20,570
There were so many incidents like that.

128
00:09:22,910 --> 00:09:26,190
So that's why you knew these were in emergency rooms.

129
00:09:28,230 --> 00:09:31,430
That money ...

130
