Someone told me that Grandma had claimed insurance for me.

131
00:09:36,300 --> 00:09:41,040
I was young, so I didn't even think of looking through the documents.

132
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:45,240
There's no way to find that person anymore.

133
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:48,840
I don't have the courage to face you anymore.

134
