But ... today, after hearing what happened,

138
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:05,410
I think it is because of me.

139
00:10:05,410 --> 00:10:09,270
If I had just stopped grandma from going there that day,

140
00:10:09,270 --> 00:10:12,260
