Well, it is all my fault.

143
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:32,210
But ... what kind of life is like this?

144
00:10:32,210 --> 00:10:37,620
Since I was born, there has never been a time when I didn't work hard.

145
00:10:37,620 --> 00:10:40,780
How come I constantly have to feel ashamed, embarrassed

146
00:10:40,780 --> 00:10:43,220
and miserable like this?

147
00:10:43,220 --> 00:10:46,740
I hate it so much. Really.

148
00:10:51,770 --> 00:10:54,360
It's understandable.

149
00:10:57,480 --> 00:11:00,640
You told me that he didn't do a good job as a dad.

150
00:11:00,640 --> 00:11:04,090
In and out of jail. Getting out when people were about to forget the incident.

151
00:11:04,090 --> 00:11:06,880
Causing problems for your grandma and you

152
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:09,250
that embarrassed you.

153
00:11:09,250 --> 00:11:12,170
Your grandmother had to make a living by herself.

154
00:11:12,170 --> 00:11:15,020
How do you know all this so well?

155
00:11:15,990 --> 00:11:18,750
Your father told me.

156
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:22,830
On top of that, you learned the truth about your dad today.

157
00:11:22,830 --> 00:11:25,670
I can understand that you hate it.

158
00:11:25,670 --> 00:11:27,570
So ...

159
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:32,310
Let's get rid of at least one of the issues.

160
00:11:33,080 --> 00:11:36,240
What do you mean?

161
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:38,970
You have to find who did that to your grandma.

162
00:11:38,970 --> 00:11:41,260
You also have to get revenge on the lawyer from then.

163
00:11:41,260 --> 00:11:45,840
You also have to hate your father, and have to act like Kang Mi Na.

164
00:11:46,670 --> 00:11:50,950
Aigoo ... You must have been struggling for so long.

165
00:11:58,530 --> 00:12:03,010
Let's get rid of at least one by starting with your hatred toward your father.

166
00:12:05,710 --> 00:12:11,170
How can I do that right away? There are things I said, things I did ...

167
00:12:11,800 --> 00:12:15,520
You said humans are complex and multidimensional.

168
00:12:16,110 --> 00:12:18,590
You said that yourself.

169
00:12:19,190 --> 00:12:23,330
So think, "That may have been me in the past, but I guess I've grown as a person,"

170
