Jeong Do Wu gave money to someone named Jang Seok Ho and told him to kill Kang Mi Na.

189
00:14:08,820 --> 00:14:11,880
It was because Kang Mi Na had something that could harm the Hanju Group.

190
00:14:11,880 --> 00:14:16,300
And you're saying that we found details of the incident from 14 years ago on her tablet?

191
00:14:16,300 --> 00:14:21,530
Yes, 14 years ago Jeong Do Wu paid Jang Seok Ho to give false testimony

192
00:14:21,530 --> 00:14:23,830
and blamed it on Yeon Ju's father.

193
00:14:23,830 --> 00:14:26,750
I'm also sure that the Hanju group committed the arson.

194
00:14:26,750 --> 00:14:28,610
So ...

195
00:14:28,610 --> 00:14:32,230
the most important thing is

196
00:14:32,230 --> 00:14:36,040
that you two aren't the children of the people

197
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:40,510
who harmed each others' parents.

198
00:14:40,510 --> 00:14:42,680
That's good.

199
00:14:42,680 --> 00:14:44,550
Is that important right now?

200
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:47,620
That is the most important thing to me.

201
00:14:48,790 --> 00:14:53,020
For today, at least, let's go home and rest comfortably.

202
00:14:53,020 --> 00:14:58,450
No way, how can I go and sleep at the Hanju family house after hearing all these stories?

203
00:14:58,450 --> 00:15:01,620
No, I'll just tell them I'm working overnight at the office,

204
00:15:01,620 --> 00:15:03,540
so cover for me, will you?

205
00:15:03,540 --> 00:15:06,090
I think we'll go to Seopyeong early in the morning anyway,

206
00:15:06,090 --> 00:15:09,160
and listen to her father's story a little more.

207
00:15:09,160 --> 00:15:11,510
Do that, then.

